Retail/Branded Marketing









	 




Are you a cardholder?



Consumer Cardholder Login      Fleet Cardholder Login


	 

	 

	 

	 

	 

	 

	 

	Alon Brands, Inc. is the retail and branded marketing subsidiary of Alon. Whether you’re filling your tank with ALON gasoline or supplying fuel for thousands of tanks…buying groceries at one of our 7-Eleven locations or running your own convenience store…
	Alon Brands is there.

	Alon Brands is a dynamic organization focused on providing the optimal convenience store and fueling experience for our customers. We market and supply ALON motor fuels to independent and company-owned retail locations. We’re also the largest licensee of 7-Eleven in the U.S., operating nearly 300 convenience stores in Central and West Texas and New Mexico.

	To learn more, visit www.AlonBrands.com.

	 

 













