Careers







We are performance driven.  We value a passion for excellence.  We value teamwork.  We value and reward hard work and dedication.
Whether you are interested in our petroleum refining segment, retail (convenience store) store segment or marketing & supply segment, we offer the opportunity to provide you with more than a job – we want to help you build a career.
